<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Html Form</title>
    <style>
        article p {
            text-align: center;
            color: #e75fc7;
        

        }

        article {
            background: #434242;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
         
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <h1>Some
        Imfortant Tags About
        Form</h1>
    <form action="post">
        <label for="files">Uplode Your Cv:</label>
        <input type="file" name="files" id="files" required multiple>
        <br>
        <br>

        <label for="browsers">Select Browser:</label>
        <input type="text" name="browsers" id="browsers" list="browser-list" placeholder="Enter Your Browser" required>
        <datalist id="browser-list">
            <option value="Safari"></option>
            <option value="Chrome"></option>
            <option value="Firefox"></option>
            <option value="Opera"></option>
        </datalist>
        <br>
        <br>
        <h1>Aside Example Below👇</h1>
        <main style="border: 2px solid black; width: 100%px;height: 400px;">
            <aside style="border: 2px solid rgb(0, 136, 255); width: 200px; height: 399px;">

                <ul style="padding: 10px;">
                    <li style="list-style: none; padding: 8px 10px;">Home</li>
                    <li style="list-style: none; padding: 8px 10px;">About</li>
                    <li style="list-style: none; padding: 8px 10px;">Skills</li>
                    <li style="list-style: none; padding: 8px 10px;">Serveses</li>
                    <li style="list-style: none; padding: 8px 10px;">Projects</li>
                    <li style="list-style: none; padding: 8px 10px;">Contact</li>
                </ul>
            </aside>
            <br><br>
            <br><br>

            <section>
                <h1 style="color: rgb(101, 22, 175);">Article Examples Below👇</h1>

                <!-- ARTICLE 1 -->
                <article style="border: 2px solid rgb(49, 49, 236); width: 100%; height: 300px; margin-bottom: 20px;">

                    <h1 style="text-align: center;">My First Web Development Journey</h1>

                    <p>
                        My name is Afghan Khattak, and I started learning web development with a big dream.
                        At first, HTML looked difficult for me, but day by day I learned new tags and elements.
                        I practiced headings, paragraphs, links, images, tables, and forms every day.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        After learning HTML, I started CSS. CSS helped me design beautiful websites with colors,
                        layouts, borders, shadows, and responsive design. I spent many hours practicing code and
                        fixing
                        errors.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Now I am improving my frontend development skills and building modern websites.
                        My goal is to become a professional full-stack web developer in the future.
                    </p>

                </article>


                <!-- ARTICLE 2 -->
                <article style="border: 2px solid rgb(43, 141, 43); width: 100%; height: 300px; margin-bottom: 20px;">

                    <h1 style="text-align: center;">How I Learned Coding</h1>

                    <p>
                        When I wrote my first HTML code, I felt very excited. I learned how websites are created
                        using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Every small project increased my confidence.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Sometimes I faced many coding errors, but I never stopped learning.
                        I searched for solutions, practiced daily, and improved my coding logic step by step.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Today, I can create forms, navigation bars, cards, responsive layouts,
                        and beautiful sections for websites. Coding became my passion and favorite skill.
                    </p>

                </article>


                <!-- ARTICLE 3 -->
                <article style="border: 2px solid rgb(212, 81, 81); width: 100%; height: 300px; margin-bottom: 20px;">

                    <h1 style="text-align: center;">My Future as a Web Developer</h1>

                    <p>
                        My future goal is to become a successful web developer and freelancer.
                        I want to create professional websites for clients around the world.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        I am currently learning advanced frontend development and responsive design.
                        In the future, I also want to learn backend technologies like Node.js and databases.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        I believe consistency and practice are the keys to success.
                        Every day I write code, learn new things, and improve my development skills.
                    </p>

                </article>

            </section>

    </form>

</body>

</html>